{"title": "Authentication", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "ftp-protocol/authentication", "html": "<h1 id=\"authentication\">Authentication</h1>\n<h2 id=\"anonymous-login\">Anonymous Login</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u '' -p ''</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.5<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span>Anonymous<span class=\"w\"> </span>Login!\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"testing-credentials\">Testing Credentials</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u 'marshall' -p 'badpassword'</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;marshall&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;badpassword&#39;</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.5<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>marshall:badpassword\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"specify-port\">Specify Port</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u 'marshall' -p 'badpassword' --port 2121</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;marshall&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;badpassword&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--port<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2121</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">2121</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.5<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">2121</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>marshall:badpassword\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Authentication Anonymous Login nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u '' -p '' nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u &#39;&#39; -p &#39;&#39; FTP 192 .168.0.10 21 192 .168.0.10 [ * ] Banner: ( vsFTPd 3 .0.5 ) FTP 192 .168.0.1", "tags": []}